text: Compsosoma monnei is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 1996. It is known from Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Compsosoma monnei. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1996
